      "content": "okay good to know. sometimes i get really bad anxiety before bed though and it feels like i need a bit more to actually shut my brain off. if i had like 3 or 4 glasses once in a while to really knock myself out would that be a problem or is that also mostly fine as long as i dont fall asleep in a weird position?",
